text: Nils Hjelmström (29 August 1915 - 17 October 2003) was a Swedish ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1915 births Category:2003 deaths Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:People from Luleå
